      "parameters": {
        "content": "## RAG Weather Report Notifier\n\n**Flow:** Google Drive folder update → download file → (1) upsert into the in-memory vector DB (Gemini embeddings), (2) extract text + Gemini LLM summarizes the revised content → send via Twilio SMS.\n\n**Setup needed:** connect a free Google Gemini (PaLM) API key, and set the Twilio SMS sender + recipient numbers.",
